OL,3,CChristmas market ban reignites York
OL,4,Cblue badge access row
OL,6,FA row over disabled access to York
OL,7,Fcity centre has been reignited after
OL,8,Fit emerged blue badge holders will be
OL,9,Fbanned in the run up to Christmas this
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FThe council says no vehicles will be
OL,13,Fallowed into the centre during the day
OL,14,Fwhile the popular Christmas market is
OL,15,Fon, on the advice of anti-terror
OL,16,Fpolice.
OL,18,FBut it has angered local residents who
OL,19,Fonly last year overturned a move which
OL,20,Fwould have seen them permanently
OL,21,Fexcluded from pedestrian areas.
