OL,3,CChristmas market ban reignites York
OL,4,Cblue badge access row
OL,6,FDisability campaigner Flick Williams
OL,7,Fsaid: "When the permanent ban was in
OL,8,Fplace it was eventually recognised
OL,9,Fthat that was a breach of disabled
OL,10,Fpeople's human rights. So our question
OL,11,Fbecomes: what makes it ok to violate
OL,12,Four human rights for five weeks of the
OL,13,Fyear?
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
