OL,3,CChristmas market ban reignites York
OL,4,Cblue badge access row
OL,6,F"The reality is that normal life
OL,7,Fcarries on for us all in those five
OL,8,Fweeks preceding Christmas and
OL,9,Fregardless of the Christmas Market,
OL,10,Fdisabled people still need to get into
OL,11,Fthe city centre to do their regular
OL,12,Fshopping, to get access to banks and
OL,13,Fbuilding societies."
OL,15,FThe previous ban on disabled parking
OL,16,Fin pedestrianised areas was introduced
OL,17,Fin 2021 to make way for bollards
OL,18,Fdesigned to deter terror attacks.
