OL,3,CChristmas market ban reignites York
OL,4,Cblue badge access row
OL,6,FYork Council's new Labour
OL,7,Fadministration reversed the decision
OL,8,Fin January.
OL,10,FCampaigners who fought the ban have
OL,11,Fnow revived their 'Reverse The Ban'
OL,12,Fcampaign.
OL,14,FBlue badge holder Diane Rowath said:
OL,15,F"The ban was reversed quite some time
OL,16,Fago now, they've had plenty of time to
OL,17,Fthink about it. And they should have
OL,18,Fmade sure that disabled people were
OL,19,Fincluded in the Christmas markets but
OL,20,Falso being able to use the city centre
OL,21,Fin the way they can usually."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
