OL,3,CChristmas market ban reignites York
OL,4,Cblue badge access row
OL,6,FThe council say they will endeavour to
OL,7,Fgive blue badge holders access to the
OL,8,Fcity centre next year but that it was
OL,9,Ftoo late to change plans for 2024.
OL,11,FExec Member for Transport at City of
OL,12,FYork Council Cllr Kate Ravilios said:
OL,13,F"The arrangements for the Christmas
OL,14,Fmarket happen many months in advance
OL,15,Fand so to unravel that at this point
OL,16,Fin time would have been too complex
OL,17,Fand really expensive.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
